Instead of accessing "api/form/query" directly, use this:  https://va.ghe.com/software/LEAF-Developer-Examples/blob/master/forms/formQuery.md
Also recommend integrating its "onProgress" function to provide user feedback when dealing with large data sets
This file documents a key component in our system that helps us provide performant API responses
Use JavaScript Template literals instead of string concatenation
This makes it easier for people to work with the code (AI is very good at doing this conversion automatically)
Use async/await patterns
